E-Commerce Web Application

About

A full-stack E-Commerce Web Application that allows users to browse products, add items to a cart, place orders, and track purchases. The application includes secure user authentication, role-based access control, product management, and database integration for storing products and orders.

Features
User Registration and Login
Role-Based Access (Admin/User)
Product Catalog
Add to Cart Functionality
Checkout Process
Order Tracking
Product Management (Admin)
Order Management (Admin)
Responsive Design
Database Integration (MySQL/PostgreSQL/MongoDB)
Technologies Used
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
React.js
Node.js
Express.js
MongoDB / MySQL / PostgreSQL
